                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="font-bold text-sm text-blue-900 mb-1">General Office Access</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-blue-800">What you get without a lobbyist—calling the main office line, getting routed to a junior staffer, waiting for callbacks that may never come. This is what you're upgrading FROM.</p>
