      <section id="registration" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-8">
        <div class="bg-texas-blue-50 border-l-4 border-texas-blue-500 rounded-r-lg p-6 mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Registering as a Texas Lobbyist</h2>
          <p class="text-texas-blue-700 font-medium">The bureaucracy is the easy part</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p>
            Once you start getting paid to lobby, you'll need to register with the Texas Ethics Commission. This is the straightforward administrative part—the formality, not the hard work of building a practice.
          </p>

          <div class="not-prose my-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border-2 border-texas-blue-500 p-6 mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">When You're Required to Register</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">
                You must register with the Texas Ethics Commission within 5 days if, in a calendar quarter, you either:
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-900 mb-1">Compensation Threshold</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-blue-800">Receive (or are entitled to receive) <strong>more than $1,000</strong> in a calendar quarter for lobbying services</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-900 mb-1">Expenditure Threshold</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-blue-800">Spend <strong>more than $500</strong> in a calendar quarter on expenditures benefiting state officers or employees for lobbying purposes</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-border p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Step-by-Step Registration Process</h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-texas-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">Create Your TEC Account</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Visit ethics.state.tx.us and create a login through their online filing system. You'll need a valid email address and to set up security questions.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-texas-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">Complete Lobbyist Registration Form</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">File within 5 days of meeting either threshold. You'll provide personal information, business address, and designate whether you're registering as an individual or representing a firm.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-texas-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">List Each Client and Subject Matter</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">For every client you represent, disclose their name and the general subject matter areas you're lobbying on their behalf (e.g., "healthcare policy," "tax legislation," "transportation funding").</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-texas-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">File Quarterly Activity Reports</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Due the 10th day after each quarter ends. Report compensation received from each client, expenditures made, and subject matter lobbied. These are public records.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-texas-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">5</div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">Renew Registration Annually</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">As long as you remain active as a lobbyist, you must file a renewal registration each year and continue quarterly reporting.</p>
