                      <ul class="text-xs space-y-1 text-green-800 ml-4">
                        <li>• Stable salary while building practice</li>
                        <li>• Learn from senior lobbyists</li>
                        <li>• Access to firm's existing clients</li>
                        <li>• Shared office/infrastructure costs</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-3">
                      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-1">Tradeoffs:</p>
                      <ul class="text-xs space-y-1 text-amber-800 ml-4">
                        <li>• Lower income initially (salary vs. equity)</li>
                        <li>• Limited autonomy over clients/strategy</li>
                        <li>• May have non-compete restrictions</li>
                        <li>• Need to prove value to partners</li>
