        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 rounded-r-lg p-6 mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Career-Killing Mistakes to Avoid</h2>
          <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">Learn from others' failures</p>
